      <title>特朗普审判从法官允许陪审团听取有关事件开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/trump-arrives-at-court-for-start-of-his-first-criminal-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的首次刑事审判周一上午在曼哈顿开始，法官允许陪审员听取有关这位前总统涉嫌婚外情的证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/trump-arrives-at-court-for-start-of-his-first-criminal-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:08:05 GMT</pubDate>
